A couple of opengl demos using wxErlang.

image 
      Tests transfer of images between wx and opengl.

cubes  
      Contains vertex shader animations and shadow mapping.

draw_wings_models
      Loads and displays wings models exported with the example
      exporter.  Turn on the cool shader in options menu.
   
perlin_noise 
      Contains code a perlin noise shader and test/example code of 
	     
erl -make && erl -run <demomodule>

If you have something cool that you want me to include, send it to me.

/Dan